    <li>
      <b>Step 4:</b> After that please Add/Write your Gmail id in blank section.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a4.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 5:</b> After Fill out your Gmail, Please enter your “password”.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a5.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 6:</b> After that, Enter your business name, which type of
      business name you want at Google listin6 Ag. As well as we have given
      example in screenshot, have a look.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a6.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 7:</b> After adding the Business name, Click on “next button”. And
      you will show one window like this. Where you have to fill out the
      business category.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a7.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 8:</b> After adding the category of your business, you will show
      one window like this and now you have to add your location so, another
      customer visit to your office or store. So, please click the yes button,
      and then click the next button.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a8.png" alt="" />
    <li>
