      the completed address, click the next button.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a9.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 10:</b> after Fill out the completed address. You will show one
      window like this, where you have to pin your location at the map. After to
      pin your location at the map, click the on next button.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a10.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 11:</b> After the pin your location at the map, you will show one
      window like this, where you have to choose the No, I don’t button. Then
      click the next button.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a11.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 12:</b> after that, you will show one window like this. Where you
      have to add your contact number and add your website URL. But if you have
      no website yet, you can choose the Get a free website based on your info,
      option. After to add a contact number and your website, click the on next
      button.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a12.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 13:</b> after adding complete information. You will show one
      window like this. So please click on Finish button.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a13.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 14:</b> after the Finish button, you have to verify your Google
      listing by verification methods. So you have to fill the name and click
      the mail button. After the click the mail button, your verification code
      will come in your address with 12 days, which address you had used at
      Google listing.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a14.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 15:</b> after the completed this process, you will show one window
      like this. It means your verification code has process at your address.
      And click the continue button
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a15.png" alt="" />
