      <b>Step 16:</b> After this whole process, your Google business listing
      completed for your business. But now this Google business listing for
      Pending verification. It is means, your listing will not showing (live) on
      Google map.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a16.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 17:</b> So when you will receive the variation code. Then fill out
      that code at Google listing option. After entering the code, your Google
      listing will show on Google map.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a17.png" alt="" />
    <li>
