      optimize your Google business listing. Which has explained in below
      screenshots, so please have a look? And but first, you have to click the
      info tab at Google listing.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a18.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 19:</b> After clicking the info button, you have to click the
      added service area button, where you can add some more location near your
      business location.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a19.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 20:</b> after the Add service area, you have to click on Add
      hour’s button, where you can add your hours. When your shop will open and
      closed each day.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a20.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 21:</b> after the add hours, you have to click on Add business
      description button, where you can add your business description
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a21.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 22:</b> after the Add business description, you have to click on
      Add Photos button, where you can add your photo related to your business.
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a22.png" alt="" />
    <li>
      <b>Step 23:</b> as well as if you want to add your every service in Google
      business listing. Which service you offer to the customer. Yes, you can
      add each service. But first, you have to click on the service button.
    </li>

    <li>
      Now Google Listing successful done. And If you want to know to how to open
      my Google listing and where will show. So first you have opened this link
      https://www.google.com/business/ after open this link you have to log in
      with your Gmail id and password. Which you have used to create the Google
      listing time. After login, you will see, your Google listing, like this
    </li>
    <img src="../images/marketing-a23.png" alt="" />
